{"tid":657241,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"許大美人李嘉欣與老公依偎自拍 嫁豪門十年超幸福","createTime":"2018-05-08T02:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T15:39:00.000Z","uid":82917,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd28b7f58df46dad9d87fba3325f2135c1c8798","tid":657241,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:38:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>許</strong></span>大美人李嘉欣與香港富商許晉亨結婚近10年，育有7歲兒子Jayden，小倆口感情依舊甜蜜。20日李嘉欣更在微博PO出與老公恩愛照放閃，同時嫁得好門與豪門，令人稱羨。<br />\n常在網上與粉絲分享日常小確性的李嘉欣，就PO出一張在電梯間中甜蜜依偎老公的放閃照，「為週末電梯照加點紅，祝大家愉快。」小倆口散髮出的幸福氛圍連屏幕前的網友都感受到，「好美，幸福的味道撲面而來」、「女神好幸福」、「真的是嫁對了人」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/103802_85d6f3d5233bfda07ef80763adc3c699.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F103802_85d6f3d5233bfda07ef80763adc3c699.png&h=649eb53f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"248625172c7be9b5e4bfb72483a6cdf7fe6f7b7e","tid":657241,"uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:38:32.000Z","msg":"個記者識唔識架，囝囝叫Jayden Max呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小JM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c1d88344da92c6458bc8c13a75c705b5b6ef94","tid":657241,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:38:58.000Z","msg":"恭喜嘉欣咁幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMy queen M"},{"pid":"7c0596ddf694626f58bf9f5808f8aa7afa33da49","tid":657241,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:51:25.000Z","msg":"召喚李嘉欣 芭比 廢事嘈 ada<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da48a8aa987d21e3e2121b2aecdfb596c1288fab","tid":657241,"uid":104555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:54:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">閪</span>